# Local secrets for `wrangler dev` / `next dev` (via initOpenNextCloudflareForDev).
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in real values for local development.
# D1 (DB) and R2 (MEDIA_BUCKET) are configured as bindings in wrangler.toml, not
# here -- this file is for secret values (API tokens, auth secrets, etc.) that
# later tasks in the CMS build will introduce. No secrets are required by Task 1.
